name: Whitsunday Jet Ski Tours
description: Discover the thrill of the Whitsundays with Ocean Dynamics, offering a variety of jet ski tour options from Airlie Beach. Our Whitsunday jet ski tours provide an exhilarating way to experience the region’s stunning beauty, crystal-clear waters, and diverse marine life. Perfect for adventure seekers, our tours promise an unforgettable journey through one of Australia’s most picturesque destinations.
includes:
Comprehensive safety briefing
All necessary equipment
Full access to Daydream Island pools and facilities (for Daydream Island Ultimate Jet Ski Adventure)
highlights:
Thrilling one-hour guided jet ski tour
Exhilarating experience through stunning beauty of Whitsundays
Exclusive private tours available
Access to Daydream Island amenities
Safety and equipment included
Perfect for adventure seekers
price_tiers: Airlie Adrenaline Jet Ski Tour: A$249 per jet ski (1 or 2 people) | Private One-Hour Tour: FROM A$1950 | Daydream Island Ultimate Jet Ski Adventure: A$425 per single passenger jet ski, A$475 for 2 passengers
